companyName: Innovator S&P 500 Ultra Buffer ETF - July
description:
The investment seeks to provide investors with returns that match those of the S&P 500 Price Index.
 The fund invests at least 80% of its net assets in FLexible EXchange® Options that reference the S&P 500 Price Return Index. The S&P 500 Price Index is a large-cap, market-weighted, U.S. equities index that tracks the price (excluding dividends) of the 500 leading companies in leading industries. The fund is non-diversified.
